Deviation from the Phase 21 §D.6 template: no script(1) log files
because interactive-TUI smoke on macOS without coreutils timeout
would add environment dependencies without tightening the trace.
Every terminal branch the TUI would exercise is pinned at the
deterministic unit level above. Future-phase TUI work can add a
play-back harness for pi-tui-specific regressions.
